  </intervention>
  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age 18-100 years old

          -  Registered patients at Mayo Clinic in Florida scheduled to undergo primary insertion
             of pacemaker

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Emergency placement of pacemaker

          -  Sub-pectoral placement of pacemaker

          -  Patients with history of chronic pain

          -  Patients with anatomical abnormality or disruption to the pacemaker insertion site or
             site of block placement

          -  Patients with allergy to local anesthetic
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
